    ["gutless","frightened","spineless","fearful","cowardly","insecure","timid","sound","bold","brave","courageous","fearless","valiant","heroic","lionhearted","epic discipline","immortal discipline","supreme discipline","extraordinary discipline","incredible discipline","unbelievable discipline","miraculous discipline","impossible discipline"],

